message.body: Have you got all my texts and the pic? Joey sent me a text that made me think you haven't?
Sorry been away from phone. Yeah I got two different texts with the pic. Joey is telling you I didn't get the pic?
No worries bud. I don't think Kristen got my first text ad then Joey forwarded one of your responses that I got...so I just wanted to make sure
Yeah Kristen doesn't get group texts with her old ass phone. He looks great especially with a natural birth. Lots of times very puffy but he is cute as can be.
Ahh--mystery solved. Yeah, he's doing well. Squished and wrinkly as all get out but so cute
Quiet time now at the hospital -- call you a little later?
Yeah no problem man. Call whenever. No rush.
